            <p><strong>Our History:</strong> Founded in 2026 right here in Liverpool, GlobalGetaways Ltd. started as a small team of passionate backpackers determined to simplify holiday planning. Over the years, we have grown into a premier travel hub, helping thousands of travelers find hidden gems across the globe.</p>
            <p><strong>Mission & Vision:</strong> Our mission is to craft and suggest unforgettable, tailor-made travel experiences. We envision a world where every traveler can access authentic, culturally rich, and hassle-free adventures, fostering a deep respect for global communities.</p>
